  "contenu": [
    {
      "id": "bd042179-58a6-4c43-952c-43aeccb0c0b7",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $f \\colon \\R^2 \\to \\R$,\n$$ (x,y) \\mapsto \\dfrac{x^2 y^2}{x^2 y^2 + (x-y)^2} $$",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f \\colon \\R^2 \\to \\R\\)</span>, <span class=\"math display\">\\[(x,y) \\mapsto \\dfrac{x^2 y^2}{x^2 y^2 + (x-y)^2}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ed4fadb4-7115-4a63-ad29-cb4314748a22",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Donner l'ensemble de définition de $f$.",
        "html": "<p>Donner l’ensemble de définition de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "b10a5231-5277-43ed-8d18-5388bd222aec",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "La fonction $f$ est définie pour tout $(x,y)\\in \\R^2$ tels que $x^2 y^2 + (x-y)^2 \\neq 0 $. Or $x^2y^2 + (x-y)^2 = 0 \\iff xy = 0 \\text{ et } x=y \\iff x=y=0$ donc $f$ est définie sur $\\R^2 \\backslash \\{(0,0)\\}$.",
        "html": "<p>La fonction <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> est définie pour tout <span class=\"math inline\">\\((x,y)\\in \\R^2\\)</span> tels que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x^2 y^2 + (x-y)^2 \\neq 0\\)</span>. Or <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x^2y^2 + (x-y)^2 = 0 \\iff xy = 0 \\text{ et } x=y \\iff x=y=0\\)</span> donc <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> est définie sur <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\R^2 \\backslash \\{(0,0)\\}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "f0b51771-18c7-41b6-b0e2-221333e837d2",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Pour $x$ fixé, calculer $g(x) = \\lim\\limits_{y \\to 0} f(x,y)$.",
        "html": "<p>Pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x\\)</span> fixé, calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(g(x) = \\lim\\limits_{y \\to 0} f(x,y)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "00ed8826-0c96-478f-91c1-70ae6e474dae",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $x \\in \\R$ : si $x=0$, $f(0,y) = 0$ et si $x \\neq 0$, $f(x,y) \\xrightarrow[y \\to 0]{} \\frac{0}{x^2} = 0$",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x \\in \\R\\)</span> : si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x=0\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(0,y) = 0\\)</span> et si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x \\neq 0\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(x,y) \\xrightarrow[y \\to 0]{} \\frac{0}{x^2} = 0\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "8d7f679c-d1ba-47c7-8d84-9e3cdd9be0e9",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Pour $y$ fixé, calculer $h(y) = \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 0} f(x,y)$.",
        "html": "<p>Pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(y\\)</span> fixé, calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(h(y) = \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 0} f(x,y)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "1646f607-b88d-481e-b0da-d5b8808badf3",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "De même, $h(y) = 0$.",
        "html": "<p>De même, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(h(y) = 0\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "270a54ef-8630-460a-94ec-d74477529fd3",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $\\lim\\limits_{x \\to 0} g(x)$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim\\limits_{x \\to 0} g(x)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "8dcb7851-fc8e-4ff2-aeaa-7e8291ba93c8",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "On en déduit que $\\lim\\limits_{x \\to 0} g(x) = 0$",
        "html": "<p>On en déduit que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim\\limits_{x \\to 0} g(x) = 0\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "0d2a10ea-9081-4e1f-8043-d0cfe9590a3a",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $\\lim\\limits_{y \\to 0} h(y)$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim\\limits_{y \\to 0} h(y)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "acaf779b-3718-4196-991a-9a460196bddd",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "De même $\\lim\\limits_{y \\to 0} h(y) = 0$",
        "html": "<p>De même <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim\\limits_{y \\to 0} h(y) = 0\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "735f1497-2cc1-4428-81ba-f1dbb1492a3a",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "La fonction $f$ admet-elle une limite quand $(x,y) \\to (0,0)$~?",
        "html": "<p>La fonction <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> admet-elle une limite quand <span class=\"math inline\">\\((x,y) \\to (0,0)\\)</span> ?</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "82305521-f0e7-40ed-abf4-b36718af9cfe",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Non car $f(x,x) = 1 \\xrightarrow[x \\to 0]{} 1$ et $f(x,0) = 0 \\xrightarrow[x \\to 0]{} 0 \\neq 1$ : on a deux chemins qui donnent deux limites différentes.",
        "html": "<p>Non car <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(x,x) = 1 \\xrightarrow[x \\to 0]{} 1\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(x,0) = 0 \\xrightarrow[x \\to 0]{} 0 \\neq 1\\)</span> : on a deux chemins qui donnent deux limites différentes.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
}